name: Nursing Cover
description: Nurse in style with My Little Maui nursing covers. Lightweight and breathable fabric; adjustable neck strap, boning at the collar allows you to make eye contact with baby while nursing. Whether to nurse with modesty or just hide the muffin top, a nursing cover makes a great gift for a new mother. Be the support a breastfeeding mother needs. Our nursing covers are hand-sewn in Maui with aloha.
